I take it Spears kissed Striker on the lips?

::Striker::

Striker blinks a few times, getting over the surprise of her kissing him. He 
opens his mouth to say something, then closes it after a few moments.

"So," he finally says, trying not to make himself look like an idiot, "What's 
the status here?"

He glances at the melted console behind Spears, knowing that it was a stupid 
question, but it was probably the best conversation he could make at that 
point.
